# Radar Data Layer

## ORM

Drizzle ORM + drizzle-kit. One schema file per domain under `src/db/schema/`.

## Catalogue graph (Postgres, not Neo4j)

```
catalogue_nodes (node_id, type, label, metadata jsonb)
catalogue_edges (edge_id, from_node_id, to_node_id, type)
```

Indexes: `(type)`, `(from_node_id, type)`, `(to_node_id, type)`.

## Query rules

- Always paginate list queries — default 20, max 100
- Prefer CTEs for graph traversals
- Never `SELECT *` without `LIMIT`
- Use parameterized queries only

## MCP

Use **Neon** MCP for branch management and SQL. Use **Context7** for Drizzle docs.
